title: RHOSLC Letting It Go

description:
Danny recaps this week's The Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, which featured the ladies arriving at Zion, a hectic dinner party, a woman named Batina making them bang on drums, and more! Danny also gives his (spoiler-free) thoughts on the new Scream!
